uientry.s:
function ManageSelection( card, click_up )
if click_up then
UIComponent( Component.Root() ):LuaCall( "ShowUnitInfoCharacterInfo", UIComponent( card ):LuaCall( "ItemAddress" ) )
end
end

function InitState(state) Component.Call("Resize", Component.Call("Width"), state.Text.DisplayHeight) Component.Call("Parent.LuaCall", "SetTextExtents", state.Text.DisplayWidth, state.Text.DisplayHeight) end

uientry.unicode: Use this slider to scroll up and down the panel.

uientry.s:
--[[ dofile( "data/ui/vertical_mousewheel_script.lua" )
local this = UIComponent( Address ) local parent = UIComponent( this:Parent( ) )
function SelectTab( tab )
parent:LuaCall( "SelectTab", tab )
end --]]
